# ASKCOS

This is the original repository for the open-source ASKCOS software. For more information, please visit the [ASKCOS GitHub](https://github.com/ASKCOS/ASKCOS).

For newer releases of ASKCOS, please see the [askcos-site](https://hub.docker.com/repository/docker/askcos/askcos-site) repository and [GitHub](https://github.com/ASKCOS/askcos-site).
